WEBVTT

00:00.877 --> 00:03.087
[waves]

00:03.087 --> 00:05.548
[swings creaking]

00:05.548 --> 00:07.842
[shutter banging]

00:07.842 --> 00:08.642
[child laughing]

00:14.056 --> 00:15.376
[footsteps]

00:17.602 --> 00:21.188
[flame sizzling]

